{"article_id":"9TAu1LaTzOUrdpK3","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"The prospect of a government shutdown Oct. 1 grew Wednesday ,","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"as the House Republican leadership promised a vote Friday on a bill","depth":9},{"id":2,"text":"that would fund government operations beyond Sept. 30 ,","depth":10},{"id":3,"text":"but also defund President Obama ' s health-care law .","depth":10},{"id":4,"text":"The maneuver reflects House Speaker John Boehner ' s acquiescence to conservatives ,","depth":9},{"id":5,"text":"who are determined to derail Obamacare","depth":10},{"id":6,"text":"before the law goes fully into effect .","depth":10},{"id":7,"text":"Enrollment of the uninsured in health plans begins Oct. 1 .","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"\" We 're going to continue to do everything","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"we can","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"to repeal the president 's failed health-care law , \"","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"Speaker Boehner said Wednesday morning .","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"The bill would also lock in across-the-board spending cuts","depth":5},{"id":13,"text":"knows as the \" sequester. \"","depth":5},{"id":14,"text":"All together , the measure is a non-starter for Democrats ,","depth":5},{"id":15,"text":"and","depth":6},{"id":16,"text":"if it passes in the Republican-run House ,","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"they promise to defeat it in the Senate ,","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"where they have the majority .","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"But Republicans will have another chance","depth":6},{"id":20,"text":"to defund the health-care law in mid-October .","depth":6},{"id":21,"text":"Then , the federal government ' s borrowing authority runs out ,","depth":6},{"id":22,"text":"and Republicans have threatened to defund Obamacare as a condition","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"for raising the debt ceiling .","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"Mr. Obama ,","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"speaking to business leaders Wednesday just a few blocks from the Capitol ,","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"reacted with fury to the Republican plan ,","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"accusing his opponents of trying to \" extort \" him","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"to achieve their goals .","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"\" You have never seen in the history of the United States the debt ceiling or the threat","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"of not raising the debt ceiling","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"being used","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"to extort a president or a governing party , \"","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"Obama told the Business Roundtable .","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"He spoke derisively of a \" faction \" of House Republicans","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"leading the charge","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"to undo health-care reform","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"and in the process , risking a government shutdown or a default on the government ' s debt .","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"The president called on the members of the Republican-leaning business group to use their influence","depth":5},{"id":39,"text":"to get Congress back to \" regular order \" in how it operates","depth":6},{"id":40,"text":"- and not in a way","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"that promises \" apocalypse \" every few months .","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"On Capitol Hill , House Republican leaders spoke with one voice ,","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"having given up in their attempt","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"to keep defunding of Obamacare separate from budget negotiations .","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"Senate Republicans were a different story .","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"Some , like Sen. Marco Rubio","depth":14},{"id":47,"text":"( R )","depth":14},{"id":48,"text":"of Florida ,","depth":13},{"id":49,"text":"applauded the House leaders","depth":12},{"id":50,"text":"and accused Obama and the Democrats of threatening to shut down the government .","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"\" The American people have made clear","depth":13},{"id":52,"text":"they want Washington to keep the government open","depth":14},{"id":53,"text":"but also need protection from Obamacare ' s harmful effects , \"","depth":14},{"id":54,"text":"Senator Rubio said .","depth":12},{"id":55,"text":"\" Today ' s announcement would accomplish what the American people have been asking of Congress . \"","depth":11},{"id":56,"text":"Others , like Sen. Lindsey Graham","depth":13},{"id":57,"text":"( R )","depth":13},{"id":58,"text":"of South Carolina , agree","depth":12},{"id":59,"text":"that Obamacare has to go ,","depth":12},{"id":60,"text":"but not at the risk of a government shutdown .","depth":12},{"id":61,"text":"`` I want to defund Obamacare .","depth":12},{"id":62,"text":"I just do n't want to cut off Social Security checks","depth":13},{"id":63,"text":"and stop paying the military , ''","depth":13},{"id":64,"text":"Senator Graham told Huffington Post .","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"Polls show","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"that","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"if the government does shut down ,","depth":11},{"id":68,"text":"the public would blame Republicans by a wide margin .","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"Last week , a CNN poll found","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"that 51 percent would blame the GOP","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"and 33 percent would blame Obama .","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"Some Republicans , like Graham , have expressed anxiety about this publicly .","depth":7},{"id":73,"text":"In 1995 and 1996 , government shutdowns ended up redounding to the benefit of then-President Clinton .","depth":6},{"id":74,"text":"But Democrats did not react gleefully to Boehner ' s announcement , at least in public .","depth":6},{"id":75,"text":"As for Obama , even before Boehner ' s capitulation to the tea party wing of his caucus , efforts","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"to woo the Republicans into a budget deal","depth":9},{"id":77,"text":"have born no fruit ,","depth":8},{"id":78,"text":"and so he has opted for verbal slaps .","depth":7},{"id":79,"text":"On Monday , the president took to a White House stage","depth":9},{"id":80,"text":"to mark the five-year anniversary of the 2008 financial crisis ,","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"and he spewed vitriol at his most ardent opponents","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"- even though a mass shooting had just taken place a few miles from the White House .","depth":9},{"id":83,"text":"`` I can not remember a time","depth":9},{"id":84,"text":"when one faction of one party promises economic chaos","depth":10},{"id":85,"text":"if it does n't get 100 percent of what it wants , ''","depth":10},{"id":86,"text":"Obama said .","depth":8},{"id":87,"text":"At Wednesday ' s briefing , White House press secretary Jay Carney suggested","depth":7},{"id":88,"text":"that the president ' s past charm offensive with Republicans","depth":9},{"id":89,"text":"- including taking some out to dinner at an expensive restaurant","depth":10},{"id":90,"text":"( on his dime ) -","depth":10},{"id":91,"text":"hadn ' t completely failed .","depth":8},{"id":92,"text":"\" What we discovered is that there is a sincere desire by Republican lawmakers , some of them , anyway ...","depth":9},{"id":93,"text":"to make budget policy","depth":10},{"id":94,"text":"that ... reduces the deficit responsibly ,","depth":11},{"id":95,"text":"but invests responsibly as well , \"","depth":11},{"id":96,"text":"Mr. Carney said .","depth":8},{"id":97,"text":"And ,","depth":9},{"id":98,"text":"he said ,","depth":9},{"id":99,"text":"the president will still try \" all manner of ways","depth":9},{"id":100,"text":"to get to yes with Republican leaders . \"","depth":9},{"id":101,"text":"Get the Monitor Stories","depth":5},{"id":102,"text":"you care about","depth":5},{"id":103,"text":"delivered to your inbox .","depth":4},{"id":104,"text":"By signing up ,","depth":4},{"id":105,"text":"you agree to our Privacy Policy","depth":4},{"id":106,"text":"But one opportunity for bonhomie has already fallen by the wayside .","depth":3},{"id":107,"text":"Wednesday night would have been the annual congressional picnic ,","depth":6},{"id":108,"text":"but a week ago , members of Congress received a blast e-mail from the White House","depth":7},{"id":109,"text":"saying the picnic had been canceled .","depth":7},{"id":110,"text":"Instead , members would be invited to bring their immediate families to the White House ' s Congressional Holiday Ball in December .","depth":6},{"id":111,"text":"Usually the event is members only .","depth":6},{"id":112,"text":"Word from the White House was that it canceled","depth":6},{"id":113,"text":"because it expected to be busy","depth":7},{"id":114,"text":"trying to get Congress to authorize airstrikes on Syria .","depth":7},{"id":115,"text":"Instead , the Syria situation has shifted to a diplomatic track ,","depth":6},{"id":116,"text":"and it ' s Washington that ' s at war .","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":233,"left":217,"right":232,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":217,"left":140,"right":216,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":140,"left":130,"right":139,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":130,"left":128,"right":129,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":128,"left":0,"right":127,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":127,"left":123,"right":126,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":123,"left":122,"right":7,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":122,"left":119,"right":121,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":119,"left":1,"right":118,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":118,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":121,"left":4,"right":120,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":120,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":126,"left":125,"right":11,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":125,"left":124,"right":10,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":124,"left":8,"right":9,"r